23#include "mpfr-impl.h"
24
25int
26mpfr_neg (mpfr_ptr a, mpfr_srcptr b, mpfr_rnd_t rnd_mode)
27{
28 if (MPFR_UNLIKELY(a != b))
29 return mpfr_set4 (a, b, rnd_mode, -MPFR_SIGN(b));
30 else
31 {
32 MPFR_CHANGE_SIGN (a);
33 if (MPFR_UNLIKELY (MPFR_IS_NAN (b)))
34 MPFR_RET_NAN;
35 else
36 MPFR_RET (0);
37 }
38}
